    "prose_paragraphs": [
      "Designers reach for Peppercorn when they want a roof that disappears into 'looks correct' rather than competing for attention. It is balanced, slightly cool, and difficult to pair badly. On a Florida house with bright sun and white stucco, it is one of the safest specifications you can write.",
